{"tid":1743194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宏觀啲睇一定要投泛民 五毛冚家剷","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T05:44:09.000Z","uid":31520,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4c29b179e75e9157baaee0a781483e0684c5098a","tid":1743194,"uid":31520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:58:09.000Z","msg":"咩理由都好 一定投泛民<br />\n唔通對泛民有唔滿意既地方 就寧願投白票放生比十惡不赦既中共建制派入去加速賣港？ 咩邏輯？<br />\n如果你會咁做 一係五毛 一係弱智<br />\n記住投泛民唔一定要你buy佢地個套<br />\n係為左唔好比建制入去加速赤化<br />\n仲有如果泛民係食人血饅頭 <br />\n咁建制應該係生劏香港人 再賣比大陸享用<br />\n最後重申 投白票冇實際意義<br />\n唔會白票夠多就可以廢左個立法會<br />\n港共政權仲係度 議會一日都會運作 一日都唔可以放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75e5f21fb67c66b285d29b9f57b94e9384e6c83","tid":1743194,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"幫手推翻今個星期主線︰<br />\n團結！用你一票絕殺保皇黨 ! <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/</a>"},{"pid":"4c4e0da125587e1ffdc4eff81bf277d6221040cc","tid":1743194,"uid":65629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"Raymond表示收到<br />\n大家記住一早去投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxjsFD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxjsFD0.jpg&h=f29b8f08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d605af031f943b680550c4e96616fc5584174126","tid":1743194,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=9d54a84b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e55d833c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=fa9327d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=f95602dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"bc1b6b865d5a4392c7f316c2ec1ab80c9afa8ffa","tid":1743194,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"取唔取消區選冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n但係有都唔投就正戇鳩"},{"pid":"bdf6cc7fd156f305a77fbb86515b8fc1f8b08fc8","tid":1743194,"uid":31520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd8b73cac842e3d30aa25a3d0f92648e5e901b20","tid":1743194,"uid":31520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a68bf50acefd973b93c10582c19a7b54897c633f","tid":1743194,"uid":31520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bacff5a4dc7c0ee5a3b3edc93a215